<db:section xml:id="details">
<db:title>Detailed Description</db:title>
<db:para>The <db:link xlink:href="qml-qt3d-input-inputsettings.xml">InputSettings</db:link> component must be set as a component of the scene root entity. It stores a pointer to the object that acts as the source of input events to be handled by various input classes. For example, a Window instance can be an event source.</db:para>
